history.content:
It has recently been approved that L&S CS majors can choose between taking math 54 or EE 16B.

For purposes of declaring the CS major for students pre-fall 2015, students have to take cs 61a,b,c, 70, math 1a,1b, and math 54 OR ee 16B, however, the grade for EE 16B will not be counted towards the 3.0 GPA requirement.
history.subject: option of Math 54 or EE 16B for LSCS majors
